I was a big fan of Freshii until learning they have NO meaningful animal welfare policies. For example, while Burger King, Subway, and hundreds of other brands have adopted the standards of the Better Chicken Commitment, Freshii has not! I won't be eating at this Freshii or any other until they do.
You can ask why Freshii is falling behind competitors like La Prep, B.GOOD, and Saladworks, on a matter as important as animal welfare.
I can't believe Freshii continues to allow animal abuse. Please adopt the Better Chicken Commitment!

I am very disappointed to hear that Freshii is not willing to ban worst practices inflicted on chickens in their supply chain... This is very important, and Freshii should pay more attention to animal welfare.
